WEBVTT

00:07:00.520 --> 00:07:05.176
out of respect and gratitude
for those men and women

00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:07.560
who came to liberate us.

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:12.800
From the awareness
that sometimes only the gun

00:07:13.840 --> 00:07:17.960
can stand between good and evil.

00:07:18.880 --> 00:07:22.896
And that is why I took up the gun --

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:24.120
not to shoot,

00:07:24.840 --> 00:07:26.296
not to kill,

00:07:26.320 --> 00:07:27.640
not to destroy,

00:07:28.600 --> 00:07:31.160
but to stop those who would do evil,